        <ontology:took_place_at rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/place/1"/>
        <ontology:hasDescription>The type of innovation of this VC (Value Chain) is Endogenous and Exogenous. Numerous wood processors recently started to provide wooden houses construction as an additional service. Wooden houses are traditional in Slovak mountains. The innovation is related to New products. The land use systems involved are Forestry. The local assets include Natural and social.  </ontology:hasDescription>
    </NamedIndividual>
    


